
'''Dustbot'''是一款家用[[垃圾|垃圾]]收集[[机器人|机器人]]，可通以过[[智能电话|智能电话]]或者[[短信|短信]]向其发送指令，Dustbot收到指令后，通过[[全球定位系統|全球定位系統]]自动走到客户位置，收集垃圾并且送到垃圾桶。Dustbot还安装有环境传感器，能夠检测沿途污染程度。原型机曾在[[意大利|意大利]]、[[瑞典|瑞典]]、[[韩国|韩国]]和[[日本|日本]]进行试验，Dustbot项目由[[欧洲联盟委员会|欧洲联盟委员会]]资助。

==试验和操作==
[[File:Dustbot_Demo_Pontedera_001.jpg|thumbnail]]
Dustbot据称是世界上第一款根据指令收集垃圾的机器人<ref name=BBC>{{Cite web | title = Dustbot the street cleaning robot | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] World News | author = Duncan Kennedy | date = 2009-05-29 | accessdate = 2009-06-08 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/in_depth/8072619.stm | archive-date = 2019-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191016100245/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/in_depth/8072619.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。可以随时通过电话和[[短信|短信]]向Dustbot发送指令<ref name=STOCK>{{Cite web   |title=Robots to sweep the streets   |publisher=Stockholm News   |author=David Jonasson   |date=2009-05-23   |accessdate=2009-06-08   |url=http://www.stockholmnews.com/more.aspx?NID=3280   |deadurl=yes   |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090527122432/http://www.stockholmnews.com/more.aspx?NID=3280   |archivedate=2009-05-27   }}</ref><ref name=BBC/>。计算得到打电话者的位置后，Dustbot被派往此位置<ref name=STOCK/>。Dustbot抵达之后，用户在Dustbot面板上输入垃圾类型，然后机器人将垃圾类型指令输送到垃圾桶<ref name=STOCK/>。 然后Dustbot打开自己的垃圾仓，收集垃圾，送到指定区域<ref name=TECH>{{Cite web | title = TECH BYTES: Google gets in on e-books - 6/01/09 - San Francisco News — abc7news.com | publisher = [[ABC_News|ABC News]] Internet Ventures | author = Vinita Nair | date = 2009-06-01 | accessdate = 2009-06-08 | url = http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news/technology&id=6841933 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110604040310/http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news%2Ftechnology&id=6841933 | archive-date = 2011-06-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

Dustbot系列包括DustCart、DustClean種機器人，可以用于城市里卡车难以到达的密集区域<ref name=BBC/>，比如欧洲一些城市的老城区<ref name=TECH/>。Dustbot可以在卡车难以进入的狭窄的街道服务<ref name=TG>{{Cite web   |title=Robot garbage cart set to hit Italian streets   |publisher=TG Daily   |author=Emma Woollacott   |date=2009-05-29   |accessdate=2009-06-08   |url=http://www.tgdaily.com/content/view/42637/135/   |deadurl=yes   |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090602115635/http://www.tgdaily.com/content/view/42637/135   |archivedate=2009-06-02   }}</ref>。 DustClean机器人也可以清扫街道、吸尘和测量污染水平<ref name=STOCK/>。

==技术==
Dustcart机器人的垃圾桶的容量为{{convert|40|kg}}<ref name=TG/>。

這種機器人有不同的本地化设置，利用[[GPS|GPS]]导航<ref name=BBC/>，并结合预装的地图<ref name=TG/>，利用[[陀螺仪|陀螺仪]]保持直立，利用超声、红外和激光传感器避免与静止的或移动的障碍物相撞<ref name=BBC/>。此外它還装有许多空气质量传感器，用于检测[[空气污染|空气污染]]<ref name=TG/><ref name="DustCart air monitoring ICRA Workshop">{{Cite web | title = DustCart, a Mobile Robot for Urban Environments: Experiments of Pollution Monitoring and Mapping during Autonomous Navigation in Urban Scenarios | publisher = Proceedings of International Conference on Robotics and Automation (ICRA 2010) Workshop on Networked and Mobile Robot Olfaction in Natural, Dynamic Environments | author = Gabriele Ferri, Alessio Mondini, Alessandro Manzi, Barbara Mazzolai, Cecilia Laschi, Virgilio Mattoli, Matteo Reggente, Todor Stoyanov, Achim J. Lilienthal, Marco Lettere and Paolo Dario | date = May 2010 | accessdate =  | url = http://www.aass.oru.se/Research/mro/publications/Ferri_etal_2010-ICRA_WS10-DustCart_Mobile_Robot_Urban_Environments_Experiments_Pollution_Monitoring_Mapping_Urban_Scenarios.html | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234352/http://www.aass.oru.se/Research/mro/publications/Ferri_etal_2010-ICRA_WS10-DustCart_Mobile_Robot_Urban_Environments_Experiments_Pollution_Monitoring_Mapping_Urban_Scenarios.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，如果空气污染严重，它可以发出预警<ref name=STOCK/>。采用机器人首要原因是便于监测污染和有毒气体，尤其是对于人无法感知的气体，或者也可以将机器人用在需要测定人长时间接触的污染气体的等情况下<ref name=Airborne_Chemical_Sensing_Review>{{Cite web | title = Airborne Chemical Sensing with Mobile Robots | publisher =  | author = Achim J. Lilienthal, Amy Loutfi and Tom Duckett | date = 2006-10-01 | accessdate =  | url = http://aass.oru.se/Research/Learning/publications/Lilienthal_etal_2006-Sensors-Airborne_Chemical_Sensing_Review.html | archive-date = 2009-04-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090413132555/http://www.aass.oru.se/Research/Learning/publications/Lilienthal_etal_2006-Sensors-Airborne_Chemical_Sensing_Review.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。污染气体的分布通过统计模型计算得到<ref name=Building_GDMs>{{Cite web | title = Building Gas Concentration Gridmaps with a Mobile Robot | publisher =  | author = Achim J. Lilienthal and Tom Duckett | date = 2004-08-31 | accessdate =  | url = http://aass.oru.se/Research/Learning/publications/Lilienthal_Duckett_2004-RAS-Building_Gas_Concentration_Gridmaps_with_a_Mobile_Robot.html | archive-date = 2009-04-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090411195056/http://www.aass.oru.se/Research/Learning/publications/Lilienthal_Duckett_2004-RAS-Building_Gas_Concentration_Gridmaps_with_a_Mobile_Robot.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=SGPM_GDMs>{{Cite web | title = Learning Gas Distribution Models Using Sparse Gaussian Process Mixtures | publisher =  | author = Cyrill Stachniss, Christian Plagemann and Achim J. Lilienthal | date = April 2009 | accessdate =  | url = http://aass.oru.se/Research/Learning/publications/Stachniss_etal_2009-AuRo-Learning_Gas_Distribution_Models_using_Sparse_Gaussian_Process_Mixtures.html | archive-date = 2010-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101024201855/http://www.aass.oru.se/Research/Learning/publications/Stachniss_etal_2009-AuRo-Learning_Gas_Distribution_Models_using_Sparse_Gaussian_Process_Mixtures.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=BAYES_OG>{{Cite web | title = Mapping multiple gas/odor sources in an uncontrolled indoor environment using a Bayesian occupancy grid mapping based method | publisher = Robotics and Autonomous Systems, Volume 59, Issue 11, Pages 988–1000, Elsevier. | author = Gabriele Ferri, Michael V. Jakuba, Alessio Mondini, Virgilio Mattoli, Barbara Mazzolai, Dana R. Yoerger, Paolo Dario | date = November 2011 | accessdate =  | url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/09218890/59/11 | archive-date = 2016-10-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161002205903/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/09218890/59/11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

Dustbot系统通过无线网络与GPS和因特网通信<ref name=STOCK/>。

2010年6月15日至8月7日，两个DustCart机器人部署在意大利[[佩乔利|佩乔利]]的村庄，提供“接到指令即登门收集已分类的垃圾”的服务。这一机器人系统便于使用，服务令人满意，提高了垃圾回收率。根据2010年9月27日布鲁塞尔ICT 2010 会议的报道，其主要缺点在于“服务慢，易出交通问题，容量低”，另外，“还是有些地方进不去”<ref>{{Cite web | title = Robots for Urban Hygiene | publisher = RoboTech srl | author = Nicola Canelli | date = 2010-09-27 | accessdate = 2015-01-30 | url = http://ec.europa.eu/digital-agenda/events/cf/ict2010/document.cfm?doc_id=14608 | archive-date = 2019-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191016100259/https://ec.europa.eu/digital-single-market/events/cf/ict2010/document.cfm?doc_id=14608 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

